{"title":"Windows 修改默认安装路径","slug":"14","date":"2022-12-24T18:55:00.000Z","updated":"2023-10-03T07:06:04.375Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/14.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"方法一\"><a href=\"#方法一\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方法一\"></a>方法一</h2><ol>\n<li>将 <code>D:\\Program Files</code> 和 <code>D:\\Program Files (x86)</code> 中的文件分别移动到 <code>C:\\Program Files</code> 和 <code>C:\\Program Files (x86)</code> 中</li>\n<li>删除 <code>D:\\Program Files</code> 和 <code>D:\\Program Files (x86)</code></li>\n<li>以 <code>管理员身份</code> 运行 <code>cmd</code></li>\n<li>在 <code>cmd</code> 中输入以下内容：<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mklink /d <span class=\"token string\">\"D:\\Program Files\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"C:\\Program Files\"</span>\nmklink /d <span class=\"token string\">\"D:\\Program Files (x86)\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"C:\\Program Files (x86)\"</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li>重启电脑</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"方法二\"><a href=\"#方法二\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方法二\"></a>方法二</h2><ol>\n<li>在 <code>任意位置</code> 创建文件 <code>edit.reg</code></li>\n<li>在 <code>edit.reg</code> 中输入以下内容<pre class=\"line-numbers language-reg\" data-language=\"reg\"><code class=\"language-reg\">Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00\n\n[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion]\n\"ProgramFilesDir\"=\"D:\\\\Program Files\"\n\"CommonFilesDir\"=\"D:\\\\Program Files\\\\Common Files\"\n\"ProgramFilesDir (x86)\"=\"D:\\\\Program Files (x86)\"\n\"CommonFilesDir (x86)\"=\"D:\\\\Program Files (x86)\\\\Common Files\"<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li>运行 <code>edit.reg</code></li>\n</ol>\n<script src=\"https://giscus.app/client.js\" data-repo=\"XyzComments/blog.xyz8848.com\" data-repo-id=\"R_kgDOHq8Hag\" data-category=\"Comments\" data-category-id=\"DIC_kwDOHq8Has4CQRHf\" data-mapping=\"pathname\" data-reactions-enabled=\"1\" data-emit-metadata=\"0\" data-input-position=\"top\" data-theme=\"light\" data-lang=\"zh-CN\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" async=\"\">\n</script>","more":"<h2 id=\"方法一\"><a href=\"#方法一\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方法一\"></a>方法一</h2><ol>\n<li>将 <code>D:\\Program Files</code> 和 <code>D:\\Program Files (x86)</code> 中的文件分别移动到 <code>C:\\Program Files</code> 和 <code>C:\\Program Files (x86)</code> 中</li>\n<li>删除 <code>D:\\Program Files</code> 和 <code>D:\\Program Files (x86)</code></li>\n<li>以 <code>管理员身份</code> 运行 <code>cmd</code></li>\n<li>在 <code>cmd</code> 中输入以下内容：<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mklink /d <span class=\"token string\">\"D:\\Program Files\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"C:\\Program Files\"</span>\nmklink /d <span class=\"token string\">\"D:\\Program Files (x86)\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"C:\\Program Files (x86)\"</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li>重启电脑</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"方法二\"><a href=\"#方法二\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方法二\"></a>方法二</h2><ol>\n<li>在 <code>任意位置</code> 创建文件 <code>edit.reg</code></li>\n<li>在 <code>edit.reg</code> 中输入以下内容<pre class=\"line-numbers language-reg\" data-language=\"reg\"><code class=\"language-reg\">Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00\n\n[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion]\n&quot;ProgramFilesDir&quot;&#x3D;&quot;D:\\\\Program Files&quot;\n&quot;CommonFilesDir&quot;&#x3D;&quot;D:\\\\Program Files\\\\Common Files&quot;\n&quot;ProgramFilesDir (x86)&quot;&#x3D;&quot;D:\\\\Program Files (x86)&quot;\n&quot;CommonFilesDir (x86)&quot;&#x3D;&quot;D:\\\\Program Files (x86)\\\\Common Files&quot;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li>运行 <code>edit.reg</code></li>\n</ol>\n<script src=\"https://giscus.app/client.js\"\n        data-repo=\"XyzComments/blog.xyz8848.com\"\n        data-repo-id=\"R_kgDOHq8Hag\"\n        data-category=\"Comments\"\n        data-category-id=\"DIC_kwDOHq8Has4CQRHf\"\n        data-mapping=\"pathname\"\n        data-reactions-enabled=\"1\"\n        data-emit-metadata=\"0\"\n        data-input-position=\"top\"\n        data-theme=\"light\"\n        data-lang=\"zh-CN\"\n        crossorigin=\"anonymous\"\n        async>\n</script>","categories":[{"name":"实用教程","path":"api/categories/实用教程.json"},{"name":"Windows","path":"api/categories/Windows.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Windows","path":"api/tags/Windows.json"},{"name":"系统","path":"api/tags/系统.json"},{"name":"Software","path":"api/tags/Software.json"},{"name":"软件","path":"api/tags/软件.json"}]}